  "description": "专业的 Claude Code Skill，将简单指令转化为生产级 Prompt。基于 CLARITY 框架，支持 61 个提示词框架，提供质量验证和多版本输出。",
  "keywords": [
    "claude-code",
    "skill",
    "prompt",
    "prompt-engineering",
    "ai",
    "prompt-optimizer",
    "clarity-framework",
    "claude-plugin",
    "npx"
  ],
  "main": "index.js",
  "bin": {
    "prompt-optimizer": "./bin/prompt-optimizer.js",
    "prompt-optimizer-skill": "./bin/prompt-optimizer.js",
    "pos": "./bin/prompt-optimizer.js"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "test": "node -e \"console.log('请查看 tests/test-cases.md 了解测试用例')\"",
    "optimize": "node bin/prompt-optimizer.js optimize",
    "frameworks": "node bin/prompt-optimizer.js frameworks"
  },
  "files": [
    "SKILL.md",
    "README.md",
    "CHANGELOG.md",
    "VERSION",
    "claude.json",
    "bin/",
    "frameworks/",
    "tests/",
    "references/"
  ],
